From: Miri Korenblit <miriam.rachel.korenblit@intel.com>
Date: Sat, 8 Mar 2025 23:19:21 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: iwlwifi: bump FW API to 98 for BZ/SC/DR devices
Git-commit: d8bc6f24c65a1b8216717856cbc46ed904c2bb16
Patch-mainline: v6.15-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

Start supporting API versions 97 and 98 for those devices.

Signed-off-by: Miri Korenblit <miriam.rachel.korenblit@intel.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250308231427.55b5455795aa.I333f1e7fa31f9da1d40f668660c1e25b93ff469e@changeid
Signed-off-by: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
